div.div:
When talking about a Waterfall Customer on a monthly (or greater) release cycle.
Things this requires:
- A lot of time
- A lot of humans
- A lot of computers (hardware)
- A lot of coordination (Marketing needs to know release date, so does finance, etc. etc.)
- A lot of management software and Ops
- A lot of late nights (always happens at the last minute)
